{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.1","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 22:1","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.021.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.022.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Achazia, roi de Juda<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-9: cf. 2 R 8:24-29; 9:1-29.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.22.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    Les habitants de J\u00e9rusalem firent r\u00e9gner \u00e0 sa place Achazia, son plus jeune fils; car la troupe venue au camp avec les Arabes avait tu\u00e9 tous les plus \u00e2g\u00e9s. Ainsi r\u00e9gna Achazia, fils de Joram, roi de Juda.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22","name":"2 Chroniques 22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.2","name":"2 Chroniques 22:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.21.20","name":"2 Chroniques 21:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.21.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.2","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 22:2","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.022.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.022.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.22.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Achazia avait quarante-deux ans lorsqu\u2019il devint roi, et il r\u00e9gna un an \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem. Sa m\u00e8re s\u2019appelait Athalie, fille d\u2019Omri.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22","name":"2 Chroniques 22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.3","name":"2 Chroniques 22:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.1","name":"2 Chroniques 22:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.3","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 22:3","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.022.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.022.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.22.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Il marcha dans les voies de la maison d\u2019Achab, car sa m\u00e8re lui donnait des conseils impies.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22","name":"2 Chroniques 22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.4","name":"2 Chroniques 22:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.2","name":"2 Chroniques 22:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.4","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 22:4","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.022.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.022.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.22.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Il fit ce qui est mal aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, comme la maison d\u2019Achab, o\u00f9 il eut apr\u00e8s la mort de son p\u00e8re des conseillers pour sa perte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22","name":"2 Chroniques 22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.5","name":"2 Chroniques 22:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.3","name":"2 Chroniques 22:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.5","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 22:5","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.022.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.022.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.22.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Entra\u00een\u00e9 par leur conseil, il alla avec Joram, fils d\u2019Achab, roi d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, \u00e0 la guerre contre Haza\u00ebl, roi de Syrie, \u00e0 Ramoth en Galaad. Et les Syriens bless\u00e8rent Joram.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22","name":"2 Chroniques 22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.6","name":"2 Chroniques 22:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.4","name":"2 Chroniques 22:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.6","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 22:6","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.022.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.022.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.22.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Joram s\u2019en retourna pour se faire gu\u00e9rir \u00e0 Jizreel des blessures que les Syriens lui avaient faites \u00e0 Rama, lorsqu\u2019il se battait contre Haza\u00ebl, roi de Syrie. Azaria, fils de Joram, roi de Juda, descendit pour voir Joram, fils d\u2019Achab, \u00e0 Jizreel, parce qu\u2019il \u00e9tait malade.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22","name":"2 Chroniques 22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.7","name":"2 Chroniques 22:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.5","name":"2 Chroniques 22:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.7","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 22:7","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.022.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.022.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.22.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Par la volont\u00e9 de Dieu, ce fut pour sa ruine qu\u2019Achazia se rendit aupr\u00e8s de Joram. Lorsqu\u2019il fut arriv\u00e9, il sortit avec Joram pour aller au-devant de J\u00e9hu, fils de Nimschi, que l\u2019\u00c9ternel avait oint pour exterminer la maison d\u2019Achab.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22","name":"2 Chroniques 22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.8","name":"2 Chroniques 22:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.6","name":"2 Chroniques 22:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.8","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 22:8","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.022.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.022.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.22.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Et comme J\u00e9hu faisait justice de la maison d\u2019Achab, il trouva les chefs de Juda et les fils des fr\u00e8res d\u2019Achazia, qui \u00e9taient au service d\u2019Achazia, et il les tua.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22","name":"2 Chroniques 22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.9","name":"2 Chroniques 22:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.7","name":"2 Chroniques 22:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.9","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 22:9","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.022.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.022.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.22.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Il chercha Achazia, et on le saisit dans Samarie, o\u00f9 il s\u2019\u00e9tait cach\u00e9. On l\u2019amena aupr\u00e8s de J\u00e9hu, et on le fit mourir. Puis ils l\u2019enterr\u00e8rent, car ils disaient: C\u2019est le fils de Josaphat, qui cherchait l\u2019\u00c9ternel de tout son c\u0153ur. Et il ne resta personne de la maison d\u2019Achazia qui f\u00fbt en \u00e9tat de r\u00e9gner.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22","name":"2 Chroniques 22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.10","name":"2 Chroniques 22:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.8","name":"2 Chroniques 22:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.10","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 22:10","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.022.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.022.011,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Athalie, reine de Juda<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 10-12: cf. 2 R 11:1-3. Pr 28:28. \u00c9s 8:17.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.22.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Athalie, m\u00e8re d\u2019Achazia, voyant que son fils \u00e9tait mort, se leva et fit p\u00e9rir toute la race royale de la maison de Juda.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22","name":"2 Chroniques 22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.11","name":"2 Chroniques 22:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.9","name":"2 Chroniques 22:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.11","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 22:11","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.022.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.022.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.22.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Mais Joschabeath, fille du roi, prit Joas, fils d\u2019Achazia, et l\u2019enleva du milieu des fils du roi, quand on les fit mourir: elle le mit avec sa nourrice dans la chambre des lits. Ainsi Joschabeath, fille du roi Joram, femme du sacrificateur Jehojada, et s\u0153ur d\u2019Achazia, le d\u00e9roba aux regards d\u2019Athalie, qui ne le fit point mourir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22","name":"2 Chroniques 22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.12","name":"2 Chroniques 22:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.10","name":"2 Chroniques 22:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.12","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 22:12","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.022.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.023.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.22.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Il resta six ans cach\u00e9 avec eux dans la maison de Dieu. Et c\u2019\u00e9tait Athalie qui r\u00e9gnait dans le pays.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22","name":"2 Chroniques 22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.23.1","name":"2 Chroniques 23:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.23.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.22.11","name":"2 Chroniques 22:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.22.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb5892e61.49972347');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb5892e61.49972347\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb5892e61.49972347","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb5892e61.49972347'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb5892e61.49972347\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}